creator: Expert Shipping Inc
descriptionHtml:
App Expert Shipping is a specialized store management application designed to better manage your shipping store. With this application, you can easily create shipments and get quotations with insurance, track their progress in real-time and handle automated claims. It also includes duties and taxes calculations to help predict shipping costs and avoid surprises.

The application also integrates with the HFPU integration with Dhl and Purolator, allowing you to manage pickups in real-time. It is also integrated with shipment creation, allowing you to efficiently manage all of your shipments.

App Expert Shipping also includes POS features such as payments, inventory and team management. It also allows you to manage country restrictions and pickups/drop-offs.
Shipment scheduling is also made easy with the application, allowing you to efficiently schedule shipments and manage inventory. Pickup and drop-off management is also streamlined, allowing you to efficiently manage your shipments.

In summary, App Expert Shipping is the ideal application for businesses of all sizes looking to streamline and automate their shipping processes, with specialized store management features and duties and taxes calculations for better cost predictions.
